“CLINK” Mobile Transfer - Using the accelerometer and clock on two mobile 
phones should allow us to arrange a transfer of DIVI between two wallets 
simply by Clinking them together.  Another option for phones that have is 
NFC (Near Field Communication)

Tools Library for Merchants and Websites: Even after 8+ years, very few 
businesses accept payment in the form of Bitcoin or other 
cryptocurrencies. We will build tools such as Wordpress and Joomla 
plugins, to make it much easier for people to accept DIVI as paymen t. 
These smart plugins will even be able to shift the DIVI price to continually 
convert to match that of a fiat currency such as US Dollar s, if the 
merchant desires.



