TOKEN SALE DETAILS
The Divi Project will sell ERC20 compliant tokens on the Ethereum blockchain 
via a smart contract. 

• Up to 60-80 million DIVX tokens will be created during the sale.

• Additional tokens, based on 20% of the total sold, will be created 
and held by The Divi Project treasury.  10% will be for influencers, 
team members, brand ambassadors, mass adoption projects and 
incentives.

• Vesting Period:  The other 10% (for founders) will vest over 2 years.

• Minimum:  5000 Ether - If for some reason we don’t reach this 
minimum target, we will return all tokens to the participants.

• Maximum Cap: 100,000 Ether - If the sale reaches the cap, the sale 
will close. 

